---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'

const achievements = [
  { label: 'Patents', value: 2 },
  { label: 'Papers Published', value: 4 },
  { label: 'Products Released', value: 6 },
  { label: 'Promotions', value: 2 },
]
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="page-container animate-fade-in">
    <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>

    <div class="content">
      <p>
        I originally studied Aerospace Engineering for my Bachelors and used my
        coding experiences in college to transition to Software Engineering as a
        career. My career started in AI/ML at Psibernetix where we worked on a
        novel technique called the Genetic Fuzzy Tree, where I advanced the
        technique by optimizing and improving features of our toolkit, as well
        as building models to apply the technique to a variety of applications.
      </p>

      <p>
        But 4 years into my career I identified some glaring holes in my
        skillset and sought out new opportunities to gain frontend, backend,
        distributed systems and cloud technologies. In my 7 years at 3 startups,
        I have seen promotions, product releases, an acquisition, layoffs and a
        company closure.
      </p>

      <p>
        Throughout my professional experiences I learned to be resilient, solve
        difficult problems, mentor engineers, and make products that users love.
        I am eager to continue learning, honing my skills, and make an impact in
        your company and the industry. Let's do great things together.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">Achievements</h2>
    <div class="achievements-grid">
      {
        achievements.map((achievement) => (
          <div class="achievement-card">
            <h3 class="achievement-label">{achievement.label}</h3>
            <p class="achievement-value">{achievement.value}</p>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-container {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .content {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .achievements-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .achievement-card {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    transition:
      transform 0.2s ease,
      box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .achievement-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .achievement-label {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .achievement-value {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
  }
</style>
